<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Peminjaman Ruangan</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen">

    <nav class="bg-white shadow-md py-4 px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="font-bold text-xl text-purple-600">Sistem Peminjaman Ruangan</div>
        <a href="/" class="bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition">Logout</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mx-auto mt-10 px-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto border-t-4 border-purple-500">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Selamat Datang di Dashboard! 🎉</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Login lu berhasil. Ini adalah halaman utama Sistem Peminjaman Ruangan.</p>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
                <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-700 text-lg">Pinjam Ruangan</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Buat pengajuan peminjaman baru.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 text-lg">Riwayat</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Cek status pengajuan lu di sini.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>